high_descs: Turn right and move to the front of the sink to face it.
Grab the cup to the left of the sink.
Turn around, walk to the wall, turn left and face the microwave.
Heat up the cup in the microwave and remove it.
Open the cupboard above the microwave on the right side.
Place the cup in the cupboard and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Heat up the cup in the microwave and put it back in the cupboard.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the covered portion of the sink, across from you.
Pick up the cup, to the left of the spoon, on the sink cover.
Turn to your left and go across the room to the wall, then turn left again and go to the microwave, across from you.
Place the cup in the microwave, heat it up, then remove it from the microwave.
Look up at the right cabinet above the microwave.
Place the cup in the right cabinet, above the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm cup in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the dishwasher then turn left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the cup that's in front of you to the left of the sink.
Turn left and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the microwave.
Warm the cup in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Look up at the cupboard above to the microwave.
Open the cabinet over the microwave and put the cup in there before closing the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm cup in the cupboard.
